{"id": 977, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受人们在机场的哪些行为？", "description": "好奇心研究所不定期会推出当季应景并充满正义感的“无！法！忍！受！”小调查，欢迎来表态。（题图来自：Oivind Hovland）", "record_count": 4935, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152313GKFdjzqVr9yIkJ1l.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-24T11:00:10Z", "options": [{"id": 81664, "content": "因为天气或管制等客观原因对地勤大呼小叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280379}, {"id": 81666, "content": "脱鞋躺着睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609279}, {"id": 81667, "content": "用四个扬声器的手机播放“苍茫的天涯是我滴爱。。。。。‘’", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619354}, {"id": 82439, "content": "后面有人说看不惯别人带走飞机餐的 真的想问是想炫耀些什么嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360430}, {"id": 81928, "content": "飞机起飞前一秒关机，飞机刚落地一秒就开机，都说了舱门打开才能开机啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235801}, {"id": 81673, "content": "熊孩子叽叽喳喳的吵闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621165}, {"id": 81677, "content": "小孩哭~！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609846}, {"id": 81678, "content": "写个牌子接机", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612033}, {"id": 81679, "content": "说打电话各种装逼的人，为什么觉得他们装逼，有那么无聊打电话假装谈生意的人吗？看你那想要却得不到的样子他就high了吗？机场应该算是离土豪最近的地方了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222387}, {"id": 81680, "content": "说话超大声，一堆人叽叽喳喳说个不停?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555487}, {"id": 81681, "content": "。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610776}, {"id": 81937, "content": "最讨厌(T ^ T)吃饭时看到有人玩脚，睡觉时叽叽咕吵个不停", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622768}, {"id": 81682, "content": "！！！", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182650dGXUJp5BZj0evLRT", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610776}, {"id": 81683, "content": "吐痰", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621362}, {"id": 81685, "content": "我不明白“我起飞了/我下地了”可以成为不能忍受的行为？给家人/朋友报平安碍着你什么了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347192}, {"id": 81686, "content": "一直说个不停，感觉在像旁边的人炫耀什么似的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613498}, {"id": 81687, "content": "熊孩子到乱跑闹腾，几个一起就更可怕了=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72844}, {"id": 81688, "content": "你好，麻烦填下调查问卷呗！你好，麻烦注册下我们公司的会员呗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620443}, {"id": 81944, "content": "我讨厌你们这些挑剔的人，", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226305}, {"id": 81947, "content": "在机场的加速扶梯站着，而不是走，有时候还是两个人并排站着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 560281}, {"id": 81693, "content": "安检我觉得越严格越好，这种大环境下，我可不愿意冒混上一个极端分子的风险。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493988}, {"id": 81694, "content": "熊孩子配上熊家长", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620622}, {"id": 81695, "content": "正常时间在机场脱了鞋躺在排椅上睡得的你咋不上天？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555870}, {"id": 81696, "content": "穷屌看你们说飞机?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616222}, {"id": 81697, "content": "没做过飞机?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562288}, {"id": 81698, "content": "熊孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601840}, {"id": 81700, "content": "机场自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621466}, {"id": 81701, "content": "自己说话很大声，小孩闹也不管。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601585}, {"id": 81702, "content": "接机的人为了省点路，总自说自话的穿过围栏", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597069}, {"id": 81703, "content": "小孩子尖叫着在椅子上踩来踩去大人也不阻止=_=", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518071}, {"id": 81704, "content": "旅游团。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346013}, {"id": 81705, "content": "迟到就插队的，我凭什么让你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66359}, {"id": 81706, "content": "迟到就插队的，我就觉得凭什么我就要让你啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66359}, {"id": 81708, "content": "坐飞机的大妈群", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618827}, {"id": 83247, "content": "泡方便面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354792}, {"id": 81712, "content": "当道", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621520}, {"id": 81716, "content": "插排的人，尤其是在国外，觉得身为中国人很丢人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608473}, {"id": 81717, "content": "经济舱的他们总探头探脑看我们头等舱", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559319}, {"id": 81718, "content": "还碰到在飞机上空乘越禁止站立越是要整理行李", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608473}, {"id": 81720, "content": "小孩，婦女大聲說話", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619223}, {"id": 81976, "content": "深长接吻", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481321}, {"id": 81721, "content": "大声说话（讲电话）！真的会觉得很没有素质！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621587}, {"id": 81723, "content": "现在的机场个火车站已经没什么分别了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399475}, {"id": 81724, "content": "回答这个问题的人都装了一逼，我刚装完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399475}, {"id": 81980, "content": "机场厕所排长队，憋着等", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481321}, {"id": 81725, "content": "躺在椅子上睡觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610875}, {"id": 81726, "content": "大声喧哗，拖鞋睡觉等", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596371}, {"id": 81729, "content": "乡村老娘客行为的人，我说的是行为而不是指人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621629}, {"id": 81730, "content": "死都不关机，一直听歌，弄电脑，仿佛不改完这个邮件就会怎样一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621638}, {"id": 81731, "content": "把飞机餐吃不下的装到包包里带走，而且会问向别人要吃不完的飞机餐，太可怕了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621638}]}